text: Zemplínska may refer to: *Zemplínska Široká, village and municipality in Michalovce District in the Kosice Region of eastern Slovakia *Zemplínska šírava, dam and lake in eastern Slovakia, near the town of Michalovce *Zemplínska Nová Ves, village and municipality in the Trebišov District in the Košice Region of south-eastern Slovakia *Zemplínska Teplica, village and municipality in the Trebišov District in the Košice Region of eastern Slovakia
title: Zemplínska
